Program: Outlook
Title: The Return of the Black Death
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbqxk
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The return of Bubonic Plague - Dr Colin McEvedy explains why it is again on the rise. Also, Hari Krisha cooking theories and spirtual health, how the machine gun helped change the course of history and a look at the New York Animal Medical Centre which offers counseling for bereaved pet owners.